title: Orchards of Newburgh 2bed 1bath Apartments
posting_body: ['A pre-eminent, Michigan-based developer, investor and property manager for more than 40 years and two generations, York Properties has meticulously nurtured a reputation for impeccably-managed assets of exceptional opportunity and unparalleled value.', "Through initiative, keen market insight and conservative, well-planned growth, York Properties has established a diverse portfolio of apartment residences and manufactured home communities in some of Michigan's most highly-desired locations.", 'As a family-owned and operated company, York Properties has carefully selected its assets for long-term investment-emphasizing the capital improvements, superior amenities and high levels of personal service that foster satisfied, long-term residents and provide excellent returns for its stakeholders.', 'A lean, efficient organization, York Properties is adept at recognizing and capitalizing on market opportunities, calling upon its legacy of experience and management consistency for growth through multiple real estate cycles']
